OL,3,C'I'm not going to yield': Starmer
OL,4,Cresponds to pressure from Trump over
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has told MPs he is
OL,8,F"not going to yield" in response to
OL,9,Fcriticisms from US President Donald
OL,10,FTrump over his response to the
OL,11,Fconflict in Iran.
OL,13,FSpeaking during Wednesday's PMQs,
OL,14,FStarmer restated: "We're not going to
OL,15,Fget dragged into this war. It is not
OL,16,Four war.
OL,18,F"A lot of pressure has been applied to
OL,19,Fme to take a different course - that
OL,20,Fpressure included what happened last
OL,21,Fnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776287489
OL,3,C'I'm not going to yield': Starmer
OL,4,Cresponds to pressure from Trump over
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,F"I'm not going to change my mind. I'm
OL,8,Fnot going to yield."
OL,10,FStarmer was responding to a question
OL,11,Ffrom Lib Dem leader Sir Ed Davey, who
OL,12,Fquestioned the wisdom of sending the
OL,13,FKing on an official visit to the US to
OL,14,F"meet a man who treats our country
OL,15,Flike a mafia boss running a protection
OL,16,Fracket."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776287489
OL,3,C'I'm not going to yield': Starmer
OL,4,Cresponds to pressure from Trump over
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FDavey was referencing a call between
OL,8,FSky News and the US president on
OL,9,FTuesday, in which he spoke about the
OL,10,FKing's upcoming visit to mark the
OL,11,F250th anniversary of American
OL,12,Findependence.
OL,14,FIn the call, Trump levelled heavy
OL,15,Fcriticism on the UK-US special
OL,16,Frelationship, describing it as "the
OL,17,Frelationship where, when we asked them
OL,18,Ffor help, they were not there. When we
OL,19,Fneeded them, they were not there. When
OL,20,Fwe didn't need them, they were not
OL,21,Fthere. And they still aren't there."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
