CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776287489
OL,3,C'I'm not going to yield': Starmer
OL,4,Cresponds to pressure from Trump over
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FThe US president also appeared to
OL,8,Fthreaten the UK trade deal, stating it
OL,9,F"can always be changed."
OL,11,FAt the time, the tariffs applied to UK
OL,12,Fgoods by the US were seen as more
OL,13,Ffavourable than those of international
OL,14,Fpartners.
OL,16,F"We gave them a good trade deal.
OL,17,FBetter than I had to. Which can always
OL,18,Fbe changed," said Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
