OL,3,C'I'm not going to yield': Starmer
OL,4,Cresponds to pressure from Trump over
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FIn response to the King's upcoming
OL,13,Fvisit to the US, Starmer said: "The
OL,14,Fmonarchy is an important reminder of
OL,15,Fthe longstanding bonds and enduring
OL,16,Frelationship between our two
OL,17,Fcountries, which are far greater than
OL,18,Fanyone who occupies a particular
OL,19,Foffice at any given time."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
