OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776287489
OL,3,C'I'm not going to yield': Starmer
OL,4,Cresponds to pressure from Trump over
OL,5,CIran war
OL,7,FKing Charles and Queen Camilla are due
OL,8,Fto visit the US on an official state
OL,9,Fvisit between April 27 and April 30.
OL,11,FIt will be the first time a British
OL,12,Fmonarch has visited the US since Queen
OL,13,FElizabeth II in 2007.
OL,15,FThere will be a formal ceremonial
OL,16,Fmilitary review the following day in
OL,17,Fthe White House grounds, plus a
OL,18,Fbilateral meeting between King Charles
OL,19,Fand Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
